        {
            "id": 6238753,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 超微電腦(SMCI-US)大漲5.02%，報36.85美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>超微電腦(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SMCI:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SMCI\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SMCI-US</a>)截至台北時間15日00:25股價上漲1.76美元，報36.85美元，漲幅5.02%，成交量17,365,404（股），盤中最高價36.86美元、最低價33.69美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.39%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.33%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.68%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+1.23%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>超微電腦(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SMCI:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SMCI\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SMCI-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-6.01%</li> <li>近 1 月：-30.76%</li> <li>近 3 月：-17.71%</li> <li>近 6 月：-2.52%</li> <li>今年以來：+26.16%</li></ul></section></main>",
